  and no composer metadata.  Valid XML with intact measure structure, but the
  harmony layer is completely absent — lowest tier on the confidence ladder.
  Used to verify LOW reducibility classification (score < 45).

  divisions=1 so quarter-note duration=1, half-note duration=2, whole=4.
-->
